HEADWORD: blitzkrieg
<hw>blitz"krieg</hw> <pr>(bl⟦icr⟧tz"kr⟦emac⟧g)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[German, <ets>blitz</ets> lightning + <ets>krieg</ets> war.]</ety>
<def>an overwhelming all-out attack with infantry, armor, and air
forces, especially by surprise against an unprepared enemy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>blitzkrieg</ent>⟦br⟧

